cast members, as well as notable guest stars that appear across two different ''series''.\n* A dark grey cell indicates the character was not in the season, or that the character's presence in the season has not yet been announced.\n* An {{note label|main|M|}} indicates the actor was part of the main cast for the season.\n* A {{note label|universe|U|}} indicates the actor was in the season as an \"Arrowverse regular\".\n* A {{note label|Voice|V|}} indicates a voice-only role.\n* A number beside a character's name indicates the character is from that alternate world (i.e. a {{note label|Earth-2|2}} indicates a character from Earth-2).\n* A letter in the Further series column indicates the character has gone on to appear in another series, and links to the appropriate section for more information (A links to ''Arrow'', V links to ''Vixen'', S links to the ''Supergirl'', and L links to ''Legends of Tomorrow'').\n</blockquote>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:99%;\"\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | Character\n! style=\"width:14.8%;\" | [[List of The Flash episodes#Season 1 (2014\u201315)|Season 1<br /><small>(2014\u201315)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:14.8%;\" | [[List of The Flash episodes#Season 2 (2015\u201316)|Season 2<br /><small>(2015\u201316)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:14.8%;\" | [[List of The Flash episodes#Season 3 (2016\u201317)|Season 3<br /><small>(2016\u201317)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:14.8%;\" | [[List of The Flash episodes#Season 4 (2017\u201318)|Season 4<br /><small>(2017-18)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:14.8%;\" | [[List of The Flash episodes#Season 5 (2018\u201319)|Season 5<br /><small>(2018-19)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:14.8%;\" | [[List of The Flash episodes#Season 6 (2019\u201320)|Season 6<br /><small>(2019-20)</small>]]\n! style=\"width:10%;\" | Further series\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\" scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#ddf;\" |\n\n===Introduced in season 1===\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Gorilla Grodd (Arrowverse)|Grodd]]\n| colspan=\"