ave\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2015/03/dominic-purcell-cast-arrow-flash-spinoff-heat-wave-cw-1201393858/ |title=Dominic Purcell Joins Arrow/Flash Spinoff |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |website=Deadline Hollywood |date=March 16, 2015 |accessdate=March 16, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318041408/http://deadline.com/2015/03/dominic-purcell-cast-arrow-flash-spinoff-heat-wave-cw-1201393858/ |archivedate=March 18, 2015 }}</ref><br/>Mitchell Kummen<ref name=\"Last Refuge\">{{cite web |url=http://nerdist.com/dcs-legends-of-tomorrow-recap-last-refuge/ |title=DC'S Legends Of Tomorrow Recap: \"Last Refuge\" |last=Marnell |first=Blair |date=April 22, 2016 |publisher=The Nerdist |access-date=April 23, 2016 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423115827/http://nerdist.com/dcs-legends-of-tomorrow-recap-last-refuge/ |archivedate=April 23, 2016 }}</ref>\n| colspan=\"4\" | Dominic Purcell{{note label|main|M}}<ref name=\":1\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/tv/news/693463-vixen-to-join-legends-of-tomorrow-season-2-but-not-megalyn-echikunwoke |title=Vixen to Join Legends of Tomorrow Season 2 |date=June 8, 2016 |website=ComingSoon.net |language=en-US |access-date=June 9, 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609043758/http://www.comingsoon.net/tv/news/693463-vixen-to-join-legends-of-tomorrow-season-2-but-not-megalyn-echikunwoke |archivedate=June 9, 2016 }}</ref><ref name=\"LoTS3Cast\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Kendra Saunders<br /><small>Hawkgirl</small>\n| Ciara Ren\u00e9e{{note label|main|M|}}<ref name=\"Hawkgirl\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2015/03/arrow-flash-spinoff-hawkgirl-ciara-renee-cw-1201401280/ |title=The Arrow/Flash Spinoff Casts Ciara Ren\u00e9e As Hawkgirl |last=Damore |first=Maegan |publisher=comicbookresources.com |date=March 30, 2015 |accessdate=April 2, 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402035734/http://deadline.com/2