ef>{{cite web|last=Damore |first=Meagan |title=Legends of Tomorrow: Constantine Boards the Waverider in New Photos |url=https://www.cbr.com/legends-of-tomorrow-constantine-photos/ |website=Comic Book Resources |access-date=January 24, 2018 }}</ref>\n| colspan=\"2\" |Matt Ryan {{note label|main|M|}}\n|  rowspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |Clark Kent <br/><small>Superman{{note label|Earth-96|96}}</small>\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| Brandon Routh\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |Jefferson Pierce <br/><small>Black Lightning</small>\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:lightgrey;\" | &nbsp;\n| Cress Williams<ref name=CrisisInfinite/>\n|-\n|}\n\n==''Freedom Fighters : The Ray''==\n{{further|Freedom Fighters: The Ray#Cast and characters}}\n<blockquote class=\"toccolours\" style=\"text-align:justify; width:95%; float:center; padding: 5px; display:table; margin: 0;\">\n'''{{center|List indicator(s)}}'''\n* This table includes main cast members, as well as notable guest stars that appear across two different ''series''.\n* A dark grey cell indicates the character was not in the season, or that the character's presence in the season has not yet been announced.\n* An {{note label|main|M|}} indicates the actor was part of the main cast for the season.\n* A {{note label|Voice|V|}} indicates a voice-only role.\n* A letter in the Further series column indicates the character has gone on to appear in another series, and links to the appropriate section for more information (A links to ''Arrow'', F links to ''The Flash'', and L links to ''Legends of Tomorrow'').\n</blockquote>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:99%;\"\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | Character\n! style=\"width:37.5%;\" | Season 1<br /><small>(2017)</small>\n! style=\"width:37.5%;\" | Season 2<br /><small>(2018)</small>\n! style=\"width:10%;\" | Further series\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" scope=\"row\" style=\"background-color:#ddf;